{"top_headlines": [{"title": "中欧班列“东通道”今年通行量突破3000列", "summary": "6月6日，一列编组55辆满载食用油、汽车轮胎、铝锭等货品的回程中欧班列经由内蒙古满洲里铁路口岸入境，驶向武汉吴家山站，今年以来，中欧班列“东通道”通行班列已突破3000列。中欧班列“东通道”由满洲里、绥芬河、同江北三大铁路口岸组成，目前已形成27条稳定运行线路，通达波兰、德国、荷兰等14个国家，串联起国内长沙、郑州、成都等60余个城市。统计显示，今年1至4月，中欧班列“东通道”累计通行量占全国总量的32.1%，其中回程班列通行量占全国回程总量的41.1%。", "source_platform": "界面新闻", "hot_rank": 8, "url": "https://www.jiemian.com/article/14545441.html", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T01:33:17+00:00", "event_type": "fermenting", "_coverage_count": 1, "_coverage_platforms": ["界面新闻"], "_likely_domain": "headline", "_heat": {"fingerprint": "9161998fb641a433", "is_new": true, "is_sustained": false, "is_deep": false, "trend": "new", "heat_score": 0.6, "appearances": 1, "platforms": ["界面新闻"], "span_hours": 0.0, "rank_timeline": [{"rank": 8, "time": "2026-06-06T09:55:41.571492+08:00"}]}, "_curator_scores": {"total": 12, "pass": true}, "_needs_search": true}, {"title": "活久见！奥特曼Dario哈萨比斯同仇敌忾：DNA得查了", "summary": "科技领袖呼吁DNA安全立法", "source_platform": "量子位", "hot_rank": 9, "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2026/06/429711.html", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T06:56:03+00:00", "event_type": "fermenting", "_coverage_count": 1, "_coverage_platforms": ["量子位"], "_likely_domain": "headline", "_heat": {"fingerprint": "754fd5b68675dd08", "is_new": false, "is_sustained": true, "is_deep": false, "trend": "stable", "heat_score": 4.3, "appearances": 57, "platforms": ["量子位"], "span_hours": 11.679467351666666, "rank_timeline": [{"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:00:48.238794+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:02:26.876735+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:02:35.858955+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:02:40.063588+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:02:47.753498+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:02:57.204292+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:03:22.142687+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:06:08.150899+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:07:32.240961+08:00"}, {"rank": 9, "time": "2026-06-05T23:07:3